#. (empty)'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"An Improved Outer Tactical Vest mk2 in urban digital.  The IOTV mk2 is the "
"heavy version of the regular IOTV. It's has twice the armour plating and "
"twice the storage capacity, but it's twice as encumbering and a lot heavier "
"as a result."
msgstr ""
"一款采用城市数码迷彩的改进型外穿战术背心 mk2。IOTV mk2 是常规 IOTV "
"的重型版本，拥有双倍的装甲板和双倍的存储容量，但因此也带来双倍的妨碍和更重的重量。"

