#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"The T.A.L.O.S (Tactical Assault Light Operator Suit) is an exprimental "
"exosuit devloped for military use. It uses a revolutionary new hybrid armour"
" system composed of both kevlar and non-newtonian metalic liquids to "
"distribute the force of an impact. It's also has an incorperated exoskeleton"
" that increases the operational capacity of the wearer. It is powered by the"
" wearers movement."
msgstr ""
"T.A.L.O.S（战术突击轻量化作战服）是一款为军事用途开发的实验性外骨骼作战服。它采用革命性的新型混合装甲系统，结合凯夫拉材料和非牛顿金属液体来分散冲击力。同时内置外骨骼，可提升穿戴者的作战能力。其动力来源于穿戴者的运动。"

