#: .\gun\20x28mm.json
msgid ""
"The XM-25 is a semi-automatic grenade launcher chambered in a proprietary "
"20x28mm cartridge. It was created during the OICW increment 2 as a stand "
"alone version of the launcher on the xm-29"
msgstr "XM-25是一款半自动榴弹发射器，使用专用的20x28毫米弹药。它是在OICW第二阶段中作为XM-29上发射器的独立版本而开发的。"

