#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "IA2 CQC"
msgid_plural "IA2 CQCs"
msgstr[0] "IA2 CQC"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The IA2 is a select fire assault rifle designed to replace the aging FAL, "
"M16 A2, and HK33's that are in service with the brazilian military . It's "
"covered in picatany rails and can support a wide range of attachments. The "
"CQC variant has a 10.3 inch barrel (260mm) and accepts any STANAG pattern "
"magazines."
msgstr ""
"IA2是一款可选射击模式的突击步枪，旨在取代巴西军队中老旧的FAL、M16 "
"A2和HK33。它覆盖有皮卡汀尼导轨，可支持多种附件。CQC型号拥有10.3英寸（260毫米）枪管，并能兼容任何STANAG规格的弹匣。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "IA2 Carbine"
msgid_plural "IA2 Carbines"
msgstr[0] "IA2卡宾枪"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The IA2 carbine is a select fire assault rifle designed to replace the aging"
" FAL, M16 A2, and HK33's that are in service with the brazilian military . "
"It's covered in picatany rails and can support a wide range of attachments. "
"The carbine variant has a 14.5 inch barrel (370mm) and accepts any STANAG "
"pattern magazines."
msgstr ""
"IA2卡宾枪是一款可选射击模式的突击步枪，旨在取代巴西军队中老旧的FAL、M16 "
"A2和HK33。它覆盖有皮卡汀尼导轨，可支持多种附件。卡宾枪型号拥有14.5英寸（370毫米）枪管，并能兼容任何STANAG规格的弹匣。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "RDB"
msgid_plural "RDBs"
msgstr[0] "RDB"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"Unlike traditional bullpups, the RDB ejects the brass downwards out of the "
"weapon, making the RDB is on of the few truly ambidexterous firearms on the "
"market"
msgstr "与传统无托式步枪不同，RDB将弹壳向下抛出枪外，使其成为市场上少数真正左右手通用的枪械之一。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "M-231"
msgid_plural "M-231s"
msgstr[0] "M-231"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The m231 port firing weapon is a heavily modified M16 pattern rifle. It has "
"no stock, no sights, a threaded hand guard to screw into the firing ports on"
" US military armored vehicles, and a lucidcrously high rate of fire. It was "
"never intened to leave the vehicle it was issued with."
msgstr ""
"M-231射击孔武器是一款经过大幅改装的M16型步枪。它没有枪托和瞄具，配有螺纹护木以旋入美军装甲车辆的射击孔，并拥有极高的射速。它从未被设计用于离开其配属的车辆。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "full auto"
msgstr "全自动"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "XM-231"
msgid_plural "XM-231s"
msgstr[0] "XM-231"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The xm231 port firing weapon is a heavily modified M16 pattern rifle. unlike"
" the m231 the mx231 has a wire collapsing stock and rudamentary sights, but "
"it still has the threaded hand guard to screw into the firing ports on US "
"military armored vehicles, and a lucidcrously high rate of fire. It was "
"never intened to leave the vehicle it was issued with."
msgstr ""
"XM-231射击孔武器是一款经过大幅改装的M16型步枪。与M-231不同，XM-231配有钢丝折叠枪托和基础瞄具，但仍保留螺纹护木以旋入美军装甲车辆的射击孔，并拥有极高的射速。它从未被设计用于离开其配属的车辆。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "XM-29 OICW"
msgid_plural "XM-29 OICWs"
msgstr[0] "XM-29 OICW"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The XM-29 OICW is an expirimental rifle that was intended to replace the "
"M-16 rifles currently in service with the US military. The OICW is a "
"Selectable Assault Battle Rifle that consists of two parts. a 20x28mm HE "
"module with a barrel length of 460 mm and a modified G36 with a barrel "
"length of 250 mm. Despite increasing the available firepower of any given "
"soldier it's insanely heavy and isn't great at engaging targets at longer "
"ranges."
msgstr ""
"XM-29 "
"OICW是一款实验性步枪，旨在取代美军现役的M-16步枪。OICW是一款可选射击模式的突击战斗步枪，由两部分组成：一个枪管长460毫米的20x28毫米高爆模块，以及一个枪管长250毫米的改进型G36。尽管它能提升单兵火力，但其重量极大，且在远距离交战中表现不佳。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "semi auto"
msgstr "半自动"

#: .\gun\223.json .\gun\300blk.json
msgid "M16a1"
msgid_plural "M16a1s"
msgstr[0] "M16a1"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The first generation of the M16. Introduced in vietnam as a replacement for "
"the m14 this rifle suffered from many mechanical failures and was over all a"
" very poor weapon."
msgstr "M16的第一代型号。在越南战争中作为M14的替代品引入，这款步枪存在许多机械故障，总体而言是一款非常糟糕的武器。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "m16a1 (semi-auto)"
msgid_plural "m16a1 (semi-auto)s"
msgstr[0] "M16a1（半自动）"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The first generation of the M16. Introduced in vietnam as a replacement for "
"the m14 this rifle suffered from many mechanical failures and was over all a"
" very poor weapon. This rifle is a civilian reproduction."
msgstr "M16的第一代型号。在越南战争中作为M14的替代品引入，这款步枪存在许多机械故障，总体而言是一款非常糟糕的武器。此步枪为民用复刻版。"

#: .\gun\223.json .\gun\300blk.json
msgid "M16a1 (burst)"
msgid_plural "M16a1 (burst)s"
msgstr[0] "M16a1（点射）"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The first generation of the M16. Introduced in vietnam as a replacement for "
"the m14 this rifle suffered from many mechanical failures and was over all a"
" very poor weapon. This rifle has an a2 lower receiver giving it burst fire "
"capabilities instead of full-auto."
msgstr ""
"M16的第一代型号。在越南战争中作为M14的替代品引入，这款步枪存在许多机械故障，总体而言是一款非常糟糕的武器。此步枪采用A2下机匣，使其具备点射功能而非全自动。"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid "burst"
msgstr "连发"

#: .\gun\223.json .\gun\300blk.json
msgid "M16a1 (auto/burst)"
msgid_plural "M16a1 (auto/burst)s"
msgstr[0] "M16a1（全自动/点射）"

#: .\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"The first generation of the M16. Introduced in vietnam as a replacement for "
"the m14 this rifle suffered from many mechanical failures and was over all a"
" very poor weapon. This rifle has an a3 lower receiver giving it burst fire "
"and full-auto capabilities."
msgstr ""
"M16的第一代型号。作为M14的替代品在越南战争中引入，这款步枪存在许多机械故障，总体而言是一款非常糟糕的武器。该步枪采用A3下机匣，具备点射和全自动射击能力。"

