"aging sniper rifles that are in service with the brazilian military . It's "
"covered in picatany rails and can support a wide range of attachments. The "
"sniper variant is chambered in 7.62x51 mm, otherwise known as .308, and has "
"a 20 inch barrel (510mm). The sniper variant accepts FAL magazines just like"
" the DMR variant."
msgstr ""
"IA2狙击步枪是一款半自动精确步枪，旨在取代巴西军队中老化的狙击步枪。它全身覆盖皮卡汀尼导轨，可支持多种附件。狙击变体使用7.62×51毫米（即.308）口径，枪管长20英寸（510毫米）。与精确射手步枪变体一样，狙击变体可使用FAL弹匣。"

